    "(65) Several innovative applications have been developed using LLMs that continue to revolutionize the field of NLP.",
    "(66) (67) 3 DataOur study leveraged the Google News RSS(68) feed as a primary data source for collecting headlines of news articles which contained AI keywords.",
    "The Google News RSS feed provides a broad array of news stories across various categories and regions in an RSS (Really Simple Syndication) format, allowing users to receive updates on the latest news articles.",
    "This service was pivotal in enabling access to a wide range of AI-related news content, reflecting a broad range of casual, scientific, global, regional and opinion news-frames on AI.",
    "Data Collection MethodsWe employed a multifaceted approach and used a set of predefined parameters for querying the Google News RSS feed."
  ]
}